metadata.name: Fancy Dragons #1
metadata.description: Growth requires patience and perseverance, our needs are compatible. So endure difficulties, rest and relax - Cooperation and community, it's a fun adventure! /n/nLife on the island, it's a fantasy for me: Working for future, we all agree. There is time for coffee, to dance and to roam free, Catch up on the island, or relax if you don't agree. /n/nA fancy life, our style is that No grudge, no judgment, no filth Live tonight, Fly with me, my friend, and I will fly with you.
